data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Charming 1993-built home nestled in the heart of Belleview Highlands. This meticulously maintained residence offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and classic style. Situated on a spacious lot, this property boasts a delightful curb appeal that invites you to explore further.  Interior Features: Step inside to discover a spacious and light-filled living area with large windows that provide plenty of natural sunlight.  The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area, creating an ideal space for family gatherings and entertaining.  The kitchen features ample counter space, and a convenient breakfast bar, making meal preparation a breeze.  Three generously sized bedrooms offer comfortable accommodations, and the master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom and extra office/den flex room space for added privacy.  The home also features a bonus room that can be used as a home office, playroom, or additional bedroom, depending on your needs.  Enjoy the convenience of a laundry room and plenty of storage space throughout the home.  Exterior Features: The property boasts a well-maintained lawn with lush landscaping, creating a tranquil outdoor oasis.  A patio provides an excellent spot for outdoor dining and relaxation.  The backyard is fully fenced, offering privacy and security for family and pets.  A spacious driveway and attached garage provide ample parking space. Also a gas generator option if electrical service goes out.   This Belleview home is located in a friendly and well-established neighborhood, close to schools, parks, shopping, and dining options.  Location: Conveniently situated in the heart of Belleview, this home offers easy access to Ocala and its amenities.  The property is located in a family-friendly neighborhood with a strong sense of community.  Nearby schools, including Belleview Elementary School, make this an ideal location for families.  You'll be just a short drive away from shopping centers, medical facilities, and outdoor recreational areas.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming Belleview, Ocala home yours!   ‘PROPERTY HAS BEEN PROFESSIONALLY APPRAISED BY A LOCAL APPRAISER, much more higher than asking!”
